Statute.Title: Canada — Ukraine Free Trade Agreement Implementation Act, 2023
Statute.OtherLangTitle: (Accord de libre-échange Canada — Ukraine de 2023, Loi de mise en œuvre de l’)

CIF.Text: CIF, 2024, c. 3 in force 01.07.2024 see SI/2024-16, except,

Item.Text: — ss. 19(3), 20(2) and (4), 21(2), 22(2), 23(2), 24(2), 25(2) and 26(2) which come into force on the sixth anniversary of the day fixed by Order of the Governor in Council, see s. 40(2) and SI/2024-16 (01.07.2030) — Not in force
